title: North End 1B1B with Lots of Storage Space and W/D!
posting_body: ['Available 9/1!', 'NO BROKER FEE!', 'Ask for a link to the full video tour!', 'North End neighborhood; cozy one bedroom on a quiet street in Boston\'s "Little Italy."', 'Charming apartment with washer/dryer in-unit.', 'Located in the vibrant and historic North End of Boston with dining and entertainment options just steps away from home.', 'Short walk to Haymarket, Faneuil Hall, Quincy Market, and the Financial District with a 99/100 walk score.', 'Apartment Details:', '- 1 Bed/ 1 Bath', '- Available September 1st', '- 3 Closets - Plenty of Storage Space', '- Washer and Dryer IN-UNIT', '- Hardwood flooring', '- Kitchen features Dishwasher and Disposal', '- Central Air', '- Cat Friendly!', 'No smoking.', 'Water/sewer included; all other utilities separate.', 'First and last months rent required plus a $100 key fee.', 'No broker fee (only when you lease directly with us)!', 'Call or email to schedule your tour today!']
